																					<td align="left">
																					<p>&nbsp;</p>

																					<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><strong>It is now almost 1 year since your child took part in the National Citizen Service with The Challenge. Over the last 5 years, 50,000 young people have&nbsp;said yes to this&nbsp;opportunity and loved it. &nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>

																					<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>

																					<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">We&nbsp;want&nbsp;to let you know about an exiciting new opportunity we have - but this&nbsp;time&nbsp;it&#39;s&nbsp;aimed at you. Or - at least - your place of work.</span></span></p>

																					<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">We have recently launched&nbsp;<strong>Step Forward</strong>, our&nbsp;new apprenticeship programme&nbsp;which helps employers recruit fantastic school leavers and we&nbsp;would love to offer this opportunity to&nbsp;your organisation.&nbsp;Some organisations we have on board&nbsp;are&nbsp;Thomson Reuters,&nbsp;New Look and Comic Relief.</span></span></p>

																					<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">Step Forward is popular as it provides a great new member of staff at a very reasonable price while also, helping your place of work to do something positive about youth unemployment.</span></span></p>

																					<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">Our apprentices can work in a&nbsp;variety&nbsp;of roles including:&nbsp;administration, IT, finance and social media. Our professional day-release training develops skills and leads to&nbsp;further&nbsp;their&nbsp;<wbr />qualifications.</span></span></p>

																					<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">We have received interest from over 4,000 18-year-old&#39;s this year for just 200 places. The process is very simple as we work to find you the best three candidates &ndash; all you do is pick one.</span></span></p>

																					<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">Sound good? If you would like your place of work to consider hiring a Step Forward apprentice, we&#39;re happy to have a chat or send you more information.</span></span></p>

																					<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">Provide us with your email <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1ruQy8MyKhoWBl2FiLBhjzvuls7II8sLbMXNJ1rm-ajE/viewform">here</a> to find out more or you can reply to <a href="mailto:sf.employers@the-challenge.org">sf.employers@the-challenge.org</a></span></span></p>

																					<p style="text-align: justify;"><br />
																					&nbsp;</p>
